  "content": ". Compulsory coverage. Coverage in the State Insurance Fund shall be compulsory upon all \nemployers and their employees not over sixty (60) years of age: Provided, That an employee who is over (60) \nyears of age and paying contributions to qualify for the retirement or life insurance benefit administered by the \nSystem shall be subject to compulsory coverage.",
