  "content": ". Regional minimum wages. The minimum wage rates for agricultural and non-agricultural employees \nand workers in each and every region of the country shall be those prescribed by the Regional Tripartite \nWages and Productivity Boards. (As amended by Section 3, Republic Act No. 6727, June 9, 1989).",
